{"tid":911822,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[BU] 生日會點止玩到爆炸? 同學: 燒lin都有","createTime":"2018-11-22T07:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T13:49:09.000Z","uid":198822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b5cabf06656133f4cdc8b803b7ec481f7bdcad6d","tid":911822,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:58:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181122/58943198\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181122%2F58943198&d=qAGctaA1C1X%2F6UEGp%2F687IzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=eda554e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181122%2F58943198&h=613eacc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181122/58943198</a><br />\n<br />\n浸會大學凌晨時份發生粉塵爆炸事件﹝ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Tup1Vb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Tup1Vb&d=qAGctaA1C1X%2F6UEGp%2F687IzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=3c2e6a7d\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Tup1Vb</a> ﹞，12人受傷。有同學指，除了玩麵粉，還有玩醬油包、雀粟包，甚至打火機燒乳頭，各式各樣。<br />\n讀4年級的劉同學，今日如常上課。她認識其中一名受傷的一年級同學，據了解對方手受傷，留院治理中。<br />\n劉同學指，她不清楚事發經過，不過以往活動，確有玩麵粉，以及不同類型的玩意，包括醬油包，就是「把蕃茄醬放在同學身上」，與及雀粟包，甚至用打火機燒男同學的乳頭。<br />\n劉續說，並不是所有生日會或活動都會玩麵粉，「睇吓嗰層點玩，我嗰層只係食蛋糕，影吓相就完」。她指宿舍是不准點火"},{"pid":"e973f4351282b378b5c7c3fa608f578f326e6a2a","tid":911822,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":29,"score":-29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181122/large/1542854706_90a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181122%2Flarge%2F1542854706_90a2.jpg&h=ac2618eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劉同學"},{"pid":"b8f7aee150abe0bff9bb0b06223f7cfe812c96ba","tid":911822,"uid":170668,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2